casebody.data:
REYNOLDS et al., Appellants, v. PATTEN et al., Respondents. (City Court of New York,

General Term.

April 14, 1893.) Action by Martin Reynolds and another against Thomas Patten and another.

Argued before McGOWN, VAN WYCK, and FITZSIMONS, JJ.

Johnston & Johnston, for appellants. Deyo, Duer & Bauerdorf, for respondents. FITZSIMONS, J.

We have examined the appeal record carefully, and agree ■with the referee in his opinion and findings. Judgment is affirmed, with costs.
